snippet.textDisplay: I really appreciate the set design's reference to Edward Hopper's Nighthawks painting. It's a subtle hint at the themes of isolation/loneliness at the beginning of the music video, before the group comes all together later on. It really hits home on the transcendent power of music to connect people across the world.
